1. Zasada ne znamo kada će doći. (*Zasada*) (For now, we don't know when they will come.)
2. Ja ću zasada otići, a ti ostani. (*Zasada*) (I will leave for now, and you stay.)
3. *Zasad* ne planiram da idem na odmor. (For now, I don't plan to go on vacation.)
4. Nije *zasad* bilo nikakvih promena. (There haven't been any changes so far.)
5. *Zasad* smo još uvek u procesu pregovaranja. (For the moment, we are still in the negotiation process.)
6. Razmišljam o tome, ali *zasad* nisam donela odluku. (I am considering it, but for now, I haven't made a decision.)
7. Potrebna su mi nova saznanja, *zasad* mi je sve nejasno. (I need new information, for now, everything is unclear to me.)
8. *Zasad* nam je dovoljno hrane za sedam dana. (For now, we have enough food for seven days.)
9. Moja kompanija se *zasad* dobro kotira na tržištu. (My company is currently doing well in the market.)
10. *Zasad* mi ne smeta buka, ali možda kasnije hoće. (For now, the noise doesn't bother me, but it might later.)